1
00:00:13,919 --> 00:00:16,800
Are you saying I used to be dumb?

2
00:00:34,159 --> 00:00:34,679
How are you feeling?

3
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:38,280
What's going on?

4
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:41,079
They poisoned our food.

5
00:00:42,399 --> 00:00:43,200
Poisoned?

6
00:00:45,479 --> 00:00:47,960
I knew Lijia villagers were skilled with poisons.

7
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:50,200
But I didn't expect them to poison me.

8
00:00:52,600 --> 00:00:53,880
Here, have some water.

9
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:57,159
I poured it myself.

10
00:01:01,039 --> 00:01:02,119
They did poison us,

11
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,719
but they didn't mean to kill us.

12
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,840
If that's the case,

13
00:01:09,799 --> 00:01:11,799
they'll definitely make a move tonight.

14
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:18,560
I remember Lijia Village used to be thriving.

15
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,519
How did it turn into a ghost town?

16
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,840
I think I'm picking up a strange smell.

17
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,439
Smells like death.

18
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:56,400
You two, hurry it up!

19
00:01:56,719 --> 00:01:57,599
What's taking so long?

20
00:01:57,879 --> 00:01:58,359
Hurry, hurry!

21
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:09,560
Why is one missing?

22
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,360
Li Dong, go find it, quick!

23
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,599
Let's keep working.

24
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,199
Okay.

25
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:35,680
It's alive!

26
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:40,520
Stop yelling! You scared me to death!

27
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:40,919
Village Chief.

28
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:41,639
Quit screaming like that.

29
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,400
Chief, I can't do this job anymore.

30
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,120
Not even for money.

31
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:45,560
Yeah, same here.

32
00:02:47,719 --> 00:02:48,960
Why'd you roll down the slope?

33
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,400
Now I've got to carry you back up.

34
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:50,919
Unbelievable.

35
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:57,840
Li Dong!

36
00:02:58,479 --> 00:02:59,520
What the hell are you yelling for?

37
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:03,800
Run!

38
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:04,960
Run!

39
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,639
Did you find Li Dong yet?

40
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:54,240
Did you hear something?

41
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,280
No, nothing.

42
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,400
Ren Feifan.

43
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,680
I know you've got sharp ears and a keen nose.

44
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,360
Don't try to scare us.

45
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:05,080
I think I heard something too.

46
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:06,639
But it wasn't a human voice.

47
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:12,360
That's impossible.

48
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:15,960
Ghosts don't exist in this world.

49
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:16,920
Let's get moving.

50
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:20,839
I heard some people become ghosts when they die.

51
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,160
And others become...

52
00:04:22,199 --> 00:04:22,879
Jiangshi.

53
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:24,800
Are you out of your mind?

54
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,120
What's up with you two today?

55
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,079
So childish.

56
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,560
Let me tell you,

57
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:29,959
I don't scare easily.

58
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:32,360
Even if there really is a ghost,

59
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,360
let it show itself.

60
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,759
I'll take it on and see who's tougher.

61
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:43,439
Something's wrong.

62
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:45,560
Stay close to me.

63
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:46,680
Go!

64
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,800
What's wrong with them?

65
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,759
Are Jiangshi actually real?

66
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,120
No.

67
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,279
They're not Jiangshi.

68
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:40,959
Watch out, Feifan!

69
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:44,319
Feifan!

70
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:09,480
What caused them to end up like this?

71
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:14,000
I suspect they've all been poisoned by aconitine.

72
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,040
It's likely from long-term cultivation

73
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,879
of herbs containing aconitine.

74
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,680
That's why they've lost their minds,

75
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,839
acting like zombies.

76
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:24,480
Village Chief Li must have thought they were dead

77
00:06:24,959 --> 00:06:26,240
and hauled them here to be buried.

78
00:06:27,079 --> 00:06:28,959
He didn't expect the mountain wind

79
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:30,800
would wake these two villagers up.

80
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:34,519
The Li family in the old days,

81
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,639
if a grower fell ill from the herbs,

82
00:06:38,639 --> 00:06:40,319
would treat them until they recovered.

83
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,160
But now,

84
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:46,480
they only think about silencing witnesses.

85
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,560
Can their poisoning still be cured?

86
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:54,759
Yes.

87
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,399
But not right now,

88
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,160
or anytime soon.

89
00:06:58,879 --> 00:07:00,839
I can only temporarily restore their senses.

90
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:04,399
The toxins built up over years,

91
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:06,879
so it takes slow, steady medication to detox.

92
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:09,879
And whether they'll fully recover afterward

93
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,680
is another matter entirely.

94
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,199
So this medicine,

95
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,600
can you prescribe it?

96
00:07:18,319 --> 00:07:18,759
Of course.

97
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,160
Nannan.

98
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:27,000
Why are you here all alone?

99
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:28,319
Where's your mom?

100
00:07:28,839 --> 00:07:29,680
Where did she go?

101
00:07:30,399 --> 00:07:31,160
Mommy

102
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:34,439
was taken by the bad chief to gather herbs.

103
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:38,879
He even locked Mommy up.

104
00:07:40,079 --> 00:07:41,439
Don't cry, don't cry.

105
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,839
Do you know where your mom is?

106
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:54,040
I'm here to save you! Hurry, go!

107
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,279
Go!

108
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,800
Xixi.

109
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:04,279
Mommy!

110
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:12,920
Mommy!

111
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,639
Thank goodness you're okay.

112
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,279
I was worried sick.

113
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,320
How did you get back?

114
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,799
The Young Lady saved us.

115
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,559
Thank you, Young Lady.

116
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:41,159
Thank you, Young Lady.

117
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:41,679
Please, get up. Get up.

118
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,559
Stand up and tell me.

119
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,559
What on earth happened here?

120
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,480
How did they end up like this?

121
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,480
Four years ago,

122
00:08:51,799 --> 00:08:54,639
Village Chief Li took on a job growing Aconite

123
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:55,879
and Pinellia Rhizome from someone.

124
00:08:56,559 --> 00:08:58,360
The truth is, these herbs are all toxic.

125
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,279
Anyone who grew them

126
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:02,200
first got sores all over their body,

127
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,120
and then lost their minds.

128
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,720
Whenever a man lost his mind,

129
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,320
the chief would take him away.

130
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:09,440
Not long after,

131
00:09:09,799 --> 00:09:11,440
those men vanished completely.

132
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,440
More and more men disappeared,

133
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:15,120
and herb production couldn't keep up.

134
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,399
So he forced us women

135
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,559
to grow those poisonous herbs.

136
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,519
By the way, where's Village Chief Li?

137
00:09:26,279 --> 00:09:27,120
He's already dead.

138
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:31,679
Thank heavens!

139
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,960
Good riddance! Good riddance!

140
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:37,279
Aconite and Pinellia Rhizome are very hard to preserve.

141
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:38,960
Past their processing window,

142
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:40,720
less than one percent of their potency remains.

143
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,279
You were only in charge of growing them.

144
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:44,120
So where's the processing site?

145
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:45,360
It shouldn't be far.

146
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:46,960
That's right.

147
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,360
After the herbs were harvested,

148
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:50,120
they were sent to the old poisoner up the mountain.

149
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:52,440
Up the mountain?

150
00:09:57,240 --> 00:10:01,320
Sir, Li Mei's been a vegetable for two years now.

151
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,320
Who knows when she'll ever wake up.

152
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:05,120
If we just keep dragging this out,

153
00:10:05,159 --> 00:10:07,919
the Shen family fortune will never come to our Li family.

154
00:11:00,559 --> 00:11:01,360
Feifan.

155
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:06,639
Ever since they killed my mother,

156
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:11,480
I've always wanted to destroy the Li family myself.

157
00:11:13,679 --> 00:11:15,200
Thank you for giving me the courage

158
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:18,919
to let me

159
00:11:21,159 --> 00:11:23,200
tear off their masks with my own hands.

160
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,399
Maybe a family like the Lis should've fallen long ago.

161
00:11:30,759 --> 00:11:32,000
It'll happen just as you wish.

162
00:11:47,279 --> 00:11:48,240
Ren Feifan.

163
00:11:52,759 --> 00:11:53,639
Thank you.

164
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,000
Xu Ruojin.

165
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:17,519
Can you stop bothering the two of us?

166
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:20,120
Haven't you hurt Feifan enough already?

167
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,639
This is between Feifan and me.

168
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,120
It has nothing to do with you.

169
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,720
But he can't even stand the sight of you.

170
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,039
Can't you see that yourself?

171
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:37,120
Shen Yue, you've seen me as a rival since we were kids.

172
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,240
But in my eyes,

173
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,480
you've never even existed.

174
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:17,840
Who's there?

175
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,360
It's me.

176
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:22,360
I told you, I'm fine.

177
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:31,440
And I told you,

178
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:33,120
your wound may not be deep,

179
00:13:33,679 --> 00:13:34,600
but the toxin is unknown.

180
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:35,879
Let me check it.

181
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:36,720
No need.

182
00:13:37,799 --> 00:13:39,679
Just because I took a hit for you doesn't mean...

183
00:13:42,559 --> 00:13:45,080
Shen Yue probably needs you more.

184
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:49,320
You seem to be back to your old self.

185
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:52,360
And even more jealous now.

